{% comment %} Return Policy Page {% endcomment %}

<style>
.policy-page {
  max-width: 800px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 60px 20px;
}

.policy-page h1 {
  font-size: 2.5rem;
  color: #1a1a2e;
  margin-bottom: 40px;
  text-align: center;
  font-weight: 700;
}

.policy-page h2 {
  font-size: 1.4rem;
  color: #ff6b9d;
  margin: 35px 0 15px;
  font-weight: 600;
}

.policy-page p, .policy-page li {
  color: #555;
  line-height: 1.8;
  margin-bottom: 15px;
}

.policy-page ul {
  padding-left: 20px;
}

.policy-page li {
  margin-bottom: 10px;
}

.policy-highlight {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff5f7, #fff0f5);
  padding: 25px;
  border-radius: 15px;
  margin: 30px 0;
  border-left: 4px solid #ff6b9d;
}

.policy-contact {
  background: #f9f9f9;
  padding: 30px;
  border-radius: 15px;
  margin-top: 40px;
  text-align: center;
}

.policy-contact h3 {
  color: #1a1a2e;
  margin-bottom: 15px;
}

.policy-contact a {
  color: #ff6b9d;
  font-weight: 600;
  text-decoration: none;
}

.policy-contact a:hover {
  text-decoration: underline;
}
</style>

<div class="policy-page">
  <h1>Return & Refund Policy</h1>

  <div class="policy-highlight">
    <strong>📦 Easy Returns within 7 Days</strong><br>
    We want you to love your purchase! If you're not completely satisfied, you can return most items within 7 days of delivery.
  </div>

  <h2>Return Eligibility</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Item must be unused, unworn, and in original packaging</li>
    <li>Tags must be attached and not removed</li>
    <li>Product must be in sellable condition</li>
    <li>Customized or personalized products cannot be returned</li>
    <li>Sale/discounted items are final sale unless defective</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>How to Initiate a Return</h2>
  <ol>
    <li>Contact us on WhatsApp at <strong>+91 8383013068</strong> or email <strong>info@catfat.in</strong></li>
    <li>Provide your order number and reason for return</li>
    <li>Our team will guide you through the return process</li>
    <li>Pack the item securely in original packaging</li>
    <li>We will arrange pickup or provide return address</li>
  </ol>

  <h2>Refund Process</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Refunds are processed within 5-7 business days after we receive the returned item</li>
    <li>Refund will be credited to original payment method</li>
    <li>Shipping charges are non-refundable</li>
    <li>For defective items, full refund including shipping will be provided</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Exchange Policy</h2>
  <p>We offer exchanges for different size, color, or product. Contact us to check availability and initiate an exchange. Exchange is subject to product availability.</p>

  <h2>Non-Returnable Items</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Personalized/custom products</li>
    <li>Used or washed items</li>
    <li>Items without original tags or packaging</li>
    <li>Sale items (unless defective)</li>
    <li>Food & beverage products</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Defective or Wrong Item</h2>
  <p>If you receive a defective or wrong item, please contact us within 48 hours of delivery with photos. We will arrange for replacement or full refund at no extra cost.</p>

  <div class="policy-contact">
    <h3>Need Help?</h3>
    <p>Contact us for any return-related queries:</p>
    <p>
      📱 <a href="https://api.whatsapp.com/send?phone=918383013068">WhatsApp: +91 8383013068</a><br>
      📧 <a href="mailto:info@catfat.in">Email: info@catfat.in</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Returns Page",
  "presets": [{ "name": "Returns Page" }]
}
{% endschema %}
